         <%= image_tag("bangkok_elephant.jpg",class:"img-circle img-landing" ) %>
          <h2>Local Guides</h2>
          <p>Tour with the best local guides available.<br>Only the best and most passionate guides are listed here.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">Find guides &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <%= image_tag("family_backpack.jpg",class:"img-circle img-landing" ) %>
          <h2>Different Perspective</h2>
          <p>Not sure how to spend your precious vacation time? We'll take care of that for you.  Our guides will offer you insider information on the hottest and most fun spots in town.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <%= image_tag("singapore_skyline.jpg",class:"img-circle img-landing" ) %>
          <h2>Custom Tours</h2>
